                  <hi rendition="#i">E</hi>] aus</hi> Sie<lb/>
               <hi rendition="#b"><hi rendition="#aq">57</hi></hi><hi rendition="#aq">,</hi><hi rendition="#rkd"><hi rendition="#aq">15</hi></hi>
               <hi rendition="#aq">Emanuel, Uhlfelder, Otto. 16 <hi rendition="#g">Buch:</hi>
                  Levana.</hi>
            </p>
            <lb/>
